\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {5}{\ignorespaces MP-IDB species distribution. Left: annotation counts per \textit  {Plasmodium} species across 209 images. \textit  {P.\ falciparum} comprises 90.0\% of all annotated infected cells (1{,}267 of 1{,}407), consistent with its epidemiological prevalence. Right: proportional breakdown. The severe species imbalance mirrors the stage imbalance in BBBC041 and motivates binary (infected vs.\ uninfected) cross-dataset evaluation.}}{7}{figure.5}\protected@file@percent }
